      <div class="article-top">
                  <div itemprop="description" class="element-hidden">We think of health experts as being superhuman, but they start their day the same way most of us do: with a cup of coffee. And since seeing the way someone prepares their morning mug becomes shorthand for their nutritional philosophy, we asked 19 top experts to share their ideal way to kick-start the day.</div>
